{"list":[{"title":"目的","data":"<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">探究光反射</span></span></span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman'\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">时的规律，用实验的方法获得反射光线、入射光线与法线位置的关系。</span></span></span></span></span></p>"},{"title":"原理","data":"<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">光在同一种介质中沿直线传播。</span></span></span></span></p>"},{"title":"器材","data":"<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">激光笔、</span></span></span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman'\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">平面镜、量角器、直尺、中间可折的纸板</span></span></span></span></span></p>"},{"title":"步骤","data":"<p><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">1.提出问题</span></span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">反射光线</span></span></span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman'\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">和入射光线的位置关系如何？反射角和入射角</span></span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">之间有什么关系？</span></span></span></span></span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">2.设计实验和进行实验</span></span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">使一束光</span></span></span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman'\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">贴着纸</span></span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">板</span></span></span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman'\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">沿某一个角度射到</span>O<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">点，经平面镜反射，沿另一个方向射出。</span></span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">用量角器</span></span></span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman'\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">测量两侧的入射角和反射角，将数据记录下来。</span></span></span></span></span></p>\n\n<table cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"MsoTableGrid\" style=\"border-collapse:collapse; border:none; font-family:Calibri; font-size:13px; margin-left:9px; margin-right:9px; width:321px\">\n\t<tbody>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:1px solid black; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:1px solid black; vertical-align:top; width:113px\">\n\t\t\t<p style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">次数</span></span></span></p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:1px solid black; vertical-align:top; width:103px\">\n\t\t\t<p><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">入射角</span></span><em><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><em>i</em></span></span></em></span></p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:1px solid black; vertical-align:top; width:103px\">\n\t\t\t<p><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">反射角</span></span><em><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><em>r</em></span></span></em></span></p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:1px solid black; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; vertical-align:top; width:113px\">\n\t\t\t<p style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">1</span></span></span></p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; vertical-align:top; width:103px\">\n\t\t\t<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; vertical-align:top; width:103px\">\n\t\t\t<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:1px solid black; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; vertical-align:top; width:113px\">\n\t\t\t<p style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">2</span></span></span></p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; vertical-align:top; width:103px\">\n\t\t\t<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; vertical-align:top; width:103px\">\n\t\t\t<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:1px solid black; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; vertical-align:top; width:113px\">\n\t\t\t<p style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">3</span></span></span></p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; vertical-align:top; width:103px\">\n\t\t\t<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; vertical-align:top; width:103px\">\n\t\t\t<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t</tbody>\n</table>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体; font-size:28px\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">把纸板向前</span></span><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;; font-size:28px\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">或向后折，在纸板上还能看到反射光吗？</span></span></span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">3.分析与论证</span></span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">根据上述实验</span></span></span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman'\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">的现象和数据，试着总结光的反射定律。</span></span></span></span></span></p>"},{"title":"结论","data":"<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">在反射现象中，反射光线、入射光线和法线在同一平向内；反射光线、入射光线分居在法线两侧，反射角等于入射角。</span></span></span></span></span></p>"},{"title":"补充","data":"<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">光的反射分为镜面反射和漫反射，镜面反射和漫反射都遵循光的反射定律。</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>"}],"x":0,"y":0,"width":600,"height":600}